title: TutsPlus -  jQuery UI 301: The Widget Factory
description: Here we are, at the final installment in our jQuery UI trilogy. In this, the 301 level, we take a detailed look at the widget factory; a base class of almost all of the widgets in the framework, as well as the methods for us to build our own. For this, Dan Wellman will walk you through building a custom calculator plugin within the framework provided by the widget class. Now get ready to have some fun!
